lyrics:
5 contributorsthe world you love lyricsverse 1

hey nothing serious
we still have our fun
oh we had it once

prechorus
but windows open and close

chorus

see jimmy eat world liveget tickets as low as 249you might also likeverse 3

to rest my head

chorus
